{"id": 1912, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得在当代生活中，做哪些事情需要一些分寸？", "description": "或者说，你觉得生活中哪些烦心事的根源是“缺乏边界感”？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2526, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201709181022437piVOPCce24kuI5n.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-19T03:00:34Z", "options": [{"id": 236544, "content": "领导人身控制，简直了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134315}, {"id": 236545, "content": "看另一半的手机 自己心里要清醒  别看丢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 236546, "content": "说话，说话是一门艺术，学会说话是一门学问", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134698}, {"id": 236547, "content": "不偷瞄身边的人的手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135508}, {"id": 236803, "content": "谈恋爱不要动手动脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136366}, {"id": 236549, "content": "上来就问各种隐私，婚恋状况收入等等..告诉了答案还要被教育一番：老大不小的了，改定下来了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 237061, "content": "和人说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 236551, "content": "聊天", "image": "img/option/option/20170919120649yuGO5weiKjUvRD1T", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870877}, {"id": 236552, "content": "真心话大冒险", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904460}, {"id": 236554, "content": "对于自己看不惯的一些事发表言论", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786195}, {"id": 236555, "content": "言论", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1100195}, {"id": 236556, "content": "有场合的地方说话要有分寸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 236558, "content": "向上级反馈意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "a